data.description: Welcome to Menifee! This single story home is ready for your family. This 4 Bedroom home boast 3 Full Bathrooms. As you enter the home there is a bedroom and a bathroom to the right and an office to your left that could easily be your 5th bedroom. The Living Room is outside the office that is a good size and the formal dining area is next to it. There are 2 additional bedrooms in the rear of the home. The master bedroom is large and a get away from the rest of the home. The bathroom is also large and there are 2 walk in closets. The Kitchen is very large with a built in Island and Granite Counter Tops and there is a breakfast nook area as well. Bar stools at the island can be another area to eat or have conversation. The Family room is located near the kitchen which makes for the perfect entertainment area. Their is an indoor laundry room. The home has updated Paint, Baseboards and new flooring in the Family Room. There is a 2 car garage that has high ceilings with plenty of room for storage. Woodbine Park is across the street with access to Basketball Courts and plenty of area for kids to play.  The backyard features a large area with custom stamped concrete and a good size area for your pets/kids. This home has close access to the 215 freeway that can take you North or South quickly. Your not going to want to wait, it is time for you to make this home yours!
